      <div class="speaker__talk">
        <h3 class="speaker__talk__title">Graffiti: The Coveted Universal Web Component Format</h3>
        <p class="t-text">We love Ember, but wouldn't it be great if the components we want or create were host framework agnostic? W3C Web Components aims to do this, but it&rsquo;s missing a large part of the story. Graffiti fills in these gaps using HTMLBars, ES6/7++ syntax to let you experience the future, now. Kumbaya, all the frameworks can now hold hands.</p>
